-- Carlyle to buy J&J diagnostic unit for $4.15 bln
-- 
-- Thu Jan 16, 2014 07:58AM EST
-- None



Jan 16 (Reuters) - Privare equity firm Carlyle Group <CG.O> said it would buy Johnson & Johnson's <JNJ.N> diagnostics unit for $4.15 billion.

Carlyle said the deal was expected to close in the middle of 2014. [ID:nBw2zVLmWa]